Class GMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.atos.kawwaportal.components.components.GMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.tapestry5.ClientElement
    Deprecated. 
    This component will be removed in a future version compatible with Tapestry 5.4. We will use the component available in Tapestry5-jQuery

    public class GMap
extends Object
implements org.apache.tapestry5.ClientElement

    This Component is used to generate a GMap

    To use it, call the component as the following:
    "<div t:type="kawwa2/GMap" t:parameter="<<1>>" />"

    The fields can be filled with:

    • <<1>> : An array of JSON objects to configure the gmap3 according to the functionnalities of the jquery plugin "gmap3"
